pageContext.course_type_long_description: Join us to celebrate the Fourth of July this year with tens of thousands of LEGO pieces. Fireworks, flags, and all kinds of LEGO fun await in this one day workshop. Design and create your own unique fireworks display out of LEGO® materials, and learn about the engineering concepts that make it happen, all with the guidance of an experienced Play-Well instructor.
pageContext.course_type_name: Celebrate the Fourth of July using LEGO® Materials
